Thank you to all the Southwest Washington students who submitted an original art piece in this year’s Congressional Art Competition! The level of talent and artistry this year was truly impressive. I’m pleased to announce our 2022 winner and finalists 👇🏻

One job seeker left a nice note after attending the Jobs Fair (below): “Met some wonderful people at the Jobs Fair! Thank you so much for putting this event together. I can't wait to follow up with some of these potential employers.” 

Thanks to all for attending! 👍🏼 https://t.co/WcQTNteb0J
My top priority in Congress continues to be the health of our economy and the availability of good, family-wage jobs for folks here in Southwest Washington. https://t.co/4o4Eq05UpN

Thank you to the hundreds of employers and job seekers who came out to my 11th annual Jobs Fair today! It was great to speak with so many folks either looking for employment or business owners looking to hire. https://t.co/d0GIYcVyXx
